<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">The deadline is tomorrow morning.</font>

31
00:02:39,630 --> 00:02:40,150
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">But</font>

32
00:02:40,360 --> 00:02:42,150
