<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">♪Its petals are pierced by thorns♪</font>

121
00:06:14,840 --> 00:06:19,320
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">♪Yet it turned into a pair of wings
flying against the wind♪</font>

122
