238
00:10:38,270 --> 00:10:38,720
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Come here.</font>

239
00:10:45,750 --> 00:10:47,480
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">See, this character means "people".</font>

240
00:10:47,670 --> 00:10:48,550
