241
00:10:49,200 --> 00:10:49,960
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">People.</font>

242
00:10:50,200 --> 00:10:51,150
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">I've remembered it!</font>

243
00:10:56,270 --> 00:10:57,320
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">What are you doing here?</font>

244
