247
00:11:02,320 --> 00:11:03,960
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Please forgive us.</font>

248
00:11:17,480 --> 00:11:18,320
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Sky.</font>

