<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">People.</font>

257
00:11:36,440 --> 00:11:37,510
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">You're so clever.</font>

258
00:11:39,360 --> 00:11:41,030
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Miss, do you also want to learn to read?</font>

259
00:11:41,750 --> 00:11:43,000
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">You must be jesting with me.</font>

