<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">I-I don't have the time.</font>

261
00:11:45,510 --> 00:11:46,480
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">When you get off work,</font>

262
00:11:46,480 --> 00:11:47,150
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">if we're still here,</font>

263
00:11:47,150 --> 00:11:48,030
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">you can come over to learn.</font>

264
00:11:48,320 --> 00:11:49,600
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">But by that time,</font>

265
00:11:49,910 --> 00:11:50,790
