00:12:33,630 --> 00:12:34,390
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Zhi!</font>

283
00:12:34,600 --> 00:12:35,360
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Six.</font>

284
00:12:35,840 --> 00:12:37,600
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">I can teach reading too.</font>

285
00:12:37,870 --> 00:12:39,510
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Why do you suddenly want to teach?</font>

286
00:12:40,030 --> 00:12:41,390
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">I just asked Yanxi</font>

287
00:12:42,080 --> 00:12:43,390
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">why so many people</font>

288
00:12:43,440 --> 00:12:44,550
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">cannot read,</font>

289
00:12:45,120 --> 00:12:46,550
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">while I can since I was little.</font>

290
00:12:47,000 --> 00:12:47,870
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">What did he say?</font>

291
00:12:48,200 --> 00:12:49,630
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">He told me</font>

292
00:12:50,030 --> 00:12:51,270
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">it's because</font>

293
00:12:51,270 --> 00:12:52,480
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">my background is different from theirs.</font>

294
00:12:52,910 --> 00:12:54,960
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">My life was once supported
by the people.</font>

295
00:12:55,240 --> 00:12:55,750
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">So I was born</font>

296
00:12:55,750 --> 00:12:56,840
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">to bear more responsibilities.</font>

297
00:13:00,960 --> 00:13:02,080
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">It's not your fault.</font>

298
00:13:02,630 --> 00:13:03,390
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">No need to blame yourself.</font>

299
00:13:03,750 --> 00:13:04,440
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Yanxi,</font>

300
00:13:04,720 --> 00:13:05,510
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Zhi,</font>

301
00:13:05,630 --> 00:13:06,910
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">I want to teach them how to read.</font>

302
00:13:09,750 --> 00:13:10,390
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Alright.</font>

303
