323
00:15:07,910 --> 00:15:08,480
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Hua Ling,</font>

324
00:15:09,320 --> 00:15:10,200
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">apart from work,</font>

325
00:15:10,630 --> 00:15:11,790
