326
00:15:12,080 --> 00:15:12,960
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">I want to talk to you about.</font>

327
00:15:13,240 --> 00:15:14,120
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">What is it?</font>

328
00:15:14,720 --> 00:15:15,510
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">I...</font>

329
00:15:16,480 --> 00:15:17,790
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">I went home and talked to my aunt.</font>

330
00:15:18,200 --> 00:15:18,840
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">And I have managed</font>

331
00:15:18,840 --> 00:15:19,840
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">to save a little to support a family.</font>

332
00:15:21,480 --> 00:15:22,390
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">This time, I'm here to...</font>

333
00:15:41,600 --> 00:15:42,240
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">I wonder</font>

334
00:15:43,320 --> 00:15:44,480
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">if you're willing to have me.</font>

335
00:15:47,600 --> 00:15:48,200
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">You...</font>

336
