349
00:16:14,480 --> 00:16:16,030
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">That way, he could continue studying.</font>

350
00:16:19,720 --> 00:16:20,360
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">Yanxi,</font>

351
00:16:20,960 --> 00:16:22,320
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">after the restoration work is done,</font>

352
00:16:22,390 --> 00:16:23,480
<font face="Noto Sans S Chinese Regular" size="22">I want to continue making money.</font>

353
